==Notable accidents==
On 4 September 2024, a member of Royal Navy personnel died after a Royal Navy Merlin Mk. 4 helicopter ditched in the English Channel near Dorset while conducting night flying exercises with HMS Queen Elizabeth. The two other crew on board were taken to a hospital.

